title: JungKook [Hybrid]
body:
I will present to you Hybrid JungKook’s Fics that I prefere among those I read before so there will be no all Hybrid Fic I found ! ^^

( I will also give you author’s masterlist if you want to see their other works :)





✔️ : complete
 🔥  : smut


➤ Hybrid AU by @ravennest1342 (Masterlist 1 | 2)  ✔️

  • Hyung Line
  • Maknae Line
  • Their Collars and how they got them
  • Hybrid Biology and Facts


➤ Felicity 1 | 2 | 3 by @nochugguk (Masterlist)  🔥

     Summary : The nation breaks into a ruckus when a captive hybrid escapes the National Laboratory. Streets are empty, the city’s on a lockdown and your evening goes by idly. Until a silhouette stands at your doorstep, eyes burning like embers and lips tainted red. You know he’s a mystery you shouldn’t meddle in, but he is an intoxication you are yet to be cured of.So how far will you go to unravel secrets of a dirty world- how far will you go make him yours?


➤ Under the Bridge by @seokkbuns (Masterlist)  🔥 ✔️

      Summary : Your life takes a turn for the better one night when you find a bun under the bridge.


➤ The Fox and the Hare 1 | 2 by @guksthighs (Masterlist) ✔️

     Summary :  Jeongguk doesn’t do his homework and neither do you and you continue to guess what animal he is.


➤ Out of the Blue 1 | 2 | 3 by @imaginethisbts (Masterlist)  🔥

      Summary : Jungkook has only ever thought of his breeding clients as just that - clients, and he’s always quite indifferent to them since he only ever knows them for a short period of time. But then you come along, and he starts experiencing feelings that aren’t being manipulated by your heat. Real feelings, that he has never harbored before with anyone else.


➤ Law of the Nature 1 | 2 by @ausblack (Masterlist)  ✔️

      Summary : Jungkook hated you and you felt the same way about him. For some reason the two of you couldn’t get along; until one night, when everything changed.


➤ Cheeky Bunny by @yoongihime (Masterlist)  ✔️

      Summary : You’re a predator and he’s the prey, so what happens when the tables finally turn for our dearest bunny ?


➤ Kalopsia 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 by @erosjeon (Masterlist)

       Summary : You walk into your home one day to find your cat walking on two feet, in a human form.


➤ Tell me your secrets (I’m all ears) by @jinpire (Masterlist) ✔️

    Summary : a small rabbit shifter in a big city, you just wanted to make it through each semester with some of your dignity and grades in tact. Enter Jeon Jeongguk, the scary underclassman in your composition class. Your desk partener.

      Bonus : Nooks and naps
                    Foxie moxie (don’t pull my tail)
                    Look before you leap
                     Fluffles and kerfluffles
          


➤ Are These Real ? by @kandikorne (M.list) ✔️

   Summary : (by me, sorry) When you enter in a pet store to adopt a sweet pet, you didn’t expect to find a adorable seller who prefer you pay attention to him than bunnies in front of you.


It’s all ! ^^
I hope you will like them ! ;)
